7) Sort Top 5 Employees with Highest Salary

SELECT * FROM employees ORDER BY salary DESC LIMIT 5;



Output - 

+-------------+------------+-----------+---------------+----------+------------+------------+--------------------------+--------------+----------------------+
| employee_id | first_name | last_name | department_id | salary   | hire_date  | manager_id | email                    | phone_number | job_title            |
+-------------+------------+-----------+---------------+----------+------------+------------+--------------------------+--------------+----------------------+
|           8 | Olivia     | Jones     |             2 | 62000.00 | 2019-07-21 |          1 | olivia.jones@example.com | 555-4321     | Lead Developer       |
|          16 | Mason      | Harris    |             3 | 61000.00 | 2016-08-29 |          4 | mason.harris@example.com | 555-7891     | Senior Sales Manager |
|          11 | Alex       | White     |             1 | 61000.00 | 2020-11-23 |          1 | alex.white@example.com   | 555-2345     | HR Specialist        |
|           1 | John       | Doe       |             1 | 60000.00 | 2018-01-15 |       NULL | john.doe@example.com     | 555-1234     | Manager              |
|          28 | Avery      | Carter    |             2 | 60000.00 | 2017-12-11 |          8 | avery.carter@example.com | 555-1239     | Front-End Developer  |
+-------------+------------+-----------+---------------+----------+------------+------------+--------------------------+--------------+----------------------+












8) Sort Top 5 Employees with Highest Salary & Department_ID

SELECT * FROM employees ORDER BY salary DESC, department_id  LIMIT 5;



Output -

+-------------+------------+-----------+---------------+----------+------------+------------+--------------------------+--------------+----------------------+
| employee_id | first_name | last_name | department_id | salary   | hire_date  | manager_id | email                    | phone_number | job_title            |
+-------------+------------+-----------+---------------+----------+------------+------------+--------------------------+--------------+----------------------+
|           8 | Olivia     | Jones     |             2 | 62000.00 | 2019-07-21 |          1 | olivia.jones@example.com | 555-4321     | Lead Developer       |
|          11 | Alex       | White     |             1 | 61000.00 | 2020-11-23 |          1 | alex.white@example.com   | 555-2345     | HR Specialist        |
|          16 | Mason      | Harris    |             3 | 61000.00 | 2016-08-29 |          4 | mason.harris@example.com | 555-7891     | Senior Sales Manager |
|           1 | John       | Doe       |             1 | 60000.00 | 2018-01-15 |       NULL | john.doe@example.com     | 555-1234     | Manager              |
|          28 | Avery      | Carter    |             2 | 60000.00 | 2017-12-11 |          8 | avery.carter@example.com | 555-1239     | Front-End Developer  |
