9) It is Not Necessary to have the Order By Column as Part of Select Statement [We do not have Salary in Select Statement then too it will work]

SELECT employee_id, first_name, last_name FROM employees ORDER BY salary DESC;



Output - 

+-------------+------------+-----------+
| employee_id | first_name | last_name |
