10) We can Derive a Column as shown in below Example [We are saying the Salary for every Employee should be Increased by 10%] & We can Also do Order By on Revised Sal

SELECT *,salary + salary * .1 AS revised_salary FROM employees ORDER BY salary DESC;



OR

SELECT * FROM employees ORDER BY salary + salary * .1 DESC;




